Pip installs packages. Python packages. An easy_install replacement.

* Site: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/pip
* License: Python

Release Notes:

* Upgraded to version 1.2.1

Install with Rudix command line:

	sudo rudix install pip

Basic usage and help:

	pip help
	pip freeze

Manifest:

	/usr/local/bin/pip*
	/usr/local/share/doc/pip/
	/Library/Python/*/site-packages/pip*
